high_descs: Turn left and walk forward two steps then turn right and step forward to face the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the lettuce on the table.
Cut the head of lettuce into slices.
Turn right and step forward to face the trash can.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the trash can.
Place the lettuce slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To clean a slice of lettuce and place it in the trash can.

pick up knife on the counter top

slice lettuce on the table in front of the chair on the right
turn right walk until you reach refrigerator
put knife away in trash bin left of the refrigerator
turn around walk until you reach table, turn right to face table
pick up a slice of lettuce
turn around, walk until you reach the sink, turn left to face sink
place lettuce in the sink to the right, rinse of slice of lettuce, pick it back up
turn right walk until you reach table, turn left walk until you reach refrigerator
put slice of lettuce in trash bin to the left of the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: put a knife in a trash bin, put a clean slice of lettuce in a trash bin

high_descs: Go to face the white kitchen counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the butter knife up from the counter.
Bring the butter knife over to face the black table behind the black chair.
Cut the head of lettuce on the table in front of the chair with the knife.
Bring the knife behind the chair and face the black trash can to the left of the fridge.
Throw the knife in the trash can.
Go back to the table where the lettuce was cut.
Pick up a piece of cut lettuce from the table.
Bring the lettuce to the kitchen sink and face the sink.
Put the cut lettuce into the right side of the sink and wash it.
Pick the lettuce up from the sink and go back to face the black trash can again.
Throw the lettuce in the trash can.
